Task: Create a list of all products and their subcategories.

Table A: Production.Product (Contains the column Name)

Table B: Production.ProductSubcategory (Contains the column Name)

The Link: Both tables have a ProductSubcategoryID.




SELECT p.NAME productname, ps.name productsubcatname FROM Production.Product as p
LEFT JOIN  Production.ProductSubcategory as ps
 ON p.ProductSubcategoryID = ps.ProductSubcategoryID;

